text: "Come Back to Me" is a 1990 ballad from singer Janet Jackson. The song is about trying to bring back a romance that ended a long time ago. The song hit #2 on the Billboard Hot 100. The song was released on June 18, 1989 and is from Janet's 1989 studio album Janet Jackson's Rhythm Nation 1814 ==References== Category:1989 songs Category:1980s ballads Category:Janet Jackson songs Category:Pop ballads Category:Rhythm and blues ballads
